  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](https://gitter.im/ConsenSys/truffle?at=5cb24f22b34ccd69e7b31e2a) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nLarge repo, plenty of files.\r\n\r\nI run a single test only.\r\n\r\nAll the files are compiling (takes more than a minute)\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nRelated to: https://github.com/kleros/kleros-interaction/issues/248#issuecomment-482943506\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nI prefer if only relevant .sol files were compiled, saving me time, improving developer experience.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nWhen I run a single test, everything is compiling.\r\n\r\nI've found a workaround by moving unused files elsewhere.\r\n\r\nAnother workaround is better structuring of the repos, packages.\r\n\r\n**Or maybe the Truffle compiler can be smart enough to compile only what is needed?**",
